  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Junior Care Advisor",
  "description": "<p><strong>Junior Care Advisor (Healthcare | Client-Facing | Training Provided)</strong><br /><br /><strong>Job Summary</strong></p><p>Client-facing healthcare role supporting families with caregiver matching and care planning.</p><p><br /><strong>About the Role</strong></p><p>We are a Singapore-based live-in caregiver agency specialising in caring for elderly and adults with care needs.<br />As we expand, we are hiring <strong>Junior Care Advisors</strong> to join our care team and support families through caregiving decisions.</p><p>This role is suitable for candidates with <strong>1–2 years of experience</strong> in customer service, coordination, recruitment, or healthcare-related roles who are looking to grow into a meaningful, consultative career.<br /></p><h3><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></h3><ul><li><p>Handle enquiries from families via WhatsApp, phone, and email</p></li><li><p>Understand care needs and family preferences</p></li><li><p>Assist with matching suitable caregivers</p></li><li><p>Coordinate interviews between families and caregivers</p></li><li><p>Support administrative and MOM-related processes (training provided)</p></li><li><p>Follow up on placements and support post-placement communication</p></li><li><p>Work closely with the care operations team</p></li></ul><h3><strong>Who We’re Looking For</strong></h3><ul><li><p>Diploma or Degree holder</p></li><li><p>1–2 years experience in:</p><ul><li><p>customer service</p></li><li><p>recruitment / coordination</p></li><li><p>healthcare or social services</p></li></ul></li><li><p>Comfortable communicating clearly and professionally</p></li><li><p>Willing to learn healthcare regulations and care advisory skills<br />If you're looking to build a career with purpose and make a real difference in people’s lives, we invite you to apply today.<br /></p><p><em>Be part of a close-knit team making a difference in the lives of families and caregivers across Singapore.</em></p><p><em>Only shortlisted candidates will be contacted. Thank you for your interest.</em></p></li></ul>",
